  skullRemark: "Ugh, Boss, this... we can\u2019t let emotions get in the way, right?"
  luciferRemark: "The greatest love sometimes grows the ugliest claws.\r\n\r\n(Pause.)\r\n\r\nHe didn\u2019t hesitate. Not for a second. His child or a stranger \u2014 it wasn\u2019t even a choice.\r\n\r\nAnd that\u2019s the tragedy, isn\u2019t it? He\u2019s not wrong. Any parent would understand.\r\n\r\nBut understanding doesn\u2019t erase the old man\u2019s broken neck."
